  "response": "I don\u2019t have the capacity to create original poems that are stored or remembered, but I can certainly compose a poem for you on the spot! If you have a theme, style, or emotion in mind, let me know, and I\u2019ll craft one just for you. Here\u2019s a spontaneous example:\n\n---\n\n**Whispers of the Wind**  \n\nThe wind hums softly through the trees,  \nA melody that rides the breeze.  \nIt weaves through leaves, both young and old,  \nA story of the earth untold.  \n\nIt dances 'cross the golden plain,  \nAnd stirs the waves that rise again.  \nIt carries dreams from far away,  \nA friend unseen, yet here to stay.  \n\nSo listen close, as night descends,  \nTo secrets shared by the whispering wind.  \nIt speaks of time, both lost and found,  \nA timeless bond, a sound profound.  \n\n--- \n\nLet me know if you\u2019d like more! \ud83d\ude0a",
